getIndividualDataFromIri.HEAD: PREFIX pro: <http://www.kopbit.com/20170221144619/DWDemandExample#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
getIndividualDataFromIri.WHERE: WHERE {  &iri a ?class . ?class rdfs:subClassOf ?la. ?la owl:onProperty ?label. ?la owl:someValuesFrom ?type. &iri ?label ?date. FILTER(?class!=owl:NamedIndividual) }
